[src:agriculture-commissioner/age-of-consent-in-the-united-states-p03] (2) Sexual assault in the first degree is a Class II felony.
[src:agriculture-commissioner/age-of-consent-in-the-united-states-p03] The sentencing judge shall consider whether the actor caused serious personal injury to the victim in reaching a decision on the sentence.
